# Code Style and Size

- Keep each component/action/hook file at or below 180 lines when possible.
- Split large files by single responsibility immediately.
- Use `kebab-case` for file and folder names.
- Use `camelCase` for variables and function names.
- Write code comments in Vietnamese with diacritics when comments are needed.
- In UI labels, prefer "và" instead of "&".
- Avoid `any`; prefer explicit types or narrow unknown values.
- Keep functions focused: one function should handle one clear responsibility.
